title: EV Cherger Rental
body: EV Rental is an innovative platform connecting electric vehicle charger owners and renters. Owners list chargers for passive income and sustainable growth, while drivers find nearby chargers, easing range anxiety and boosting electric vehicle adoption. The secure platform emphasizes transparency through integrated payments and user reviews.
